1. Doctor

    Story: As a Doctor, I want to view a patient's medical history, so that I can provide accurate diagnoses and treatments.
    Story: As a Doctor, I want to manage my daily appointment schedule, so that I can optimize my workflow and reduce patient wait times.

2. Patient

    Story: As a Patient, I want to book an appointment online, so that I can schedule my visit conveniently without calling the clinic.
    Story: As a Patient, I want to receive automated appointment reminders, so that I can ensure I don't miss my scheduled consultations.

3. Admin

    Story: As an Admin, I want to manage user accounts and permissions, so that I can ensure only authorized personnel access sensitive medical data.
    Story: As an Admin, I want to generate monthly clinic performance reports, so that I can analyze patient volume and improve resource allocation.
